</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>These three pillars have not changed since 2015. What has changed is how Google measures each one — and the new AI layer that sits on top.</p>
<h3>The AI Layer: A New Visibility Battleground</h3>
<p>In 2026, Google added AI Overviews to 68% of local queries. Ask Maps launched in March 2026. And third-party AI assistants now handle 45% of local recommendation queries, up from 6% the year before.</p>
<p>The AI layer operates with different rules:</p>
