<p>The top-3 threshold is 250+ photos. But quality matters more than the raw number. Google AI image recognition systems analyze photo content. Authentic images of your team, location, and work perform better than stock photos.</p>
<p><strong>Photo upload strategy:</strong>
- Add 4-8 new photos weekly
- Include geotags when possible
- Use descriptive filenames: "downtown-dallas-plumber-fixing-leak.jpg" not "IMG_2048.jpg"
- Prioritize before/after shots for service businesses
- Add team photos, interior shots, and equipment photos
- Include photos that show your service area landmarks</p>
