<h3>The "Currently Open" Filter</h3>
<p>Google's "Open Now" filter has grown 400% since 2021. Real-time hours accuracy is now a visibility gate. If your hours are wrong and a user filters by "Open Now," you disappear.</p>
<p><strong>Hours management checklist:</strong>
- [ ] Regular hours are accurate in GBP
- [ ] Holiday hours are updated before each holiday
- [ ] Special event hours are set for known closures
- [ ] Temporary closures are marked correctly
- [ ] Hours on website match GBP exactly</p>
